text: Martin Honegger (born 20 February 1956) is a Swiss rowing coxswain. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Switzerland Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Coxswains (rowing)
